## Carnot Engine.
## Part 2
## By D. Herrick, Herrick@Nsrl31.Nsrl.Rochester.edu
## No unauthorized commercial use
## Imported Files
## ${CAPA_Tools}Problem
## Values needing defined:
## prob_val (number, e.g. /LET prob_val=1)
